10
00:02:08,550 --> 00:02:09,510
Ang bait mo.

11
00:02:10,020 --> 00:02:10,990
Ganun din ang iniisip ko.

12
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:12,270
Payagan mo akong putulin ito.

13
00:02:17,350 --> 00:02:18,190
Paano na ngayon?

14
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:20,110
Gagawin ng isang ito.

15
00:02:20,510 --> 00:02:21,350
Oo.

16
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:26,860
Simu,

17
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:28,180
gusto mo ng bagong damit?

18
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,230
Sir, alam mo ba

19
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,180
malapit na ang Void Tournament?

20
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:33,960
Dumating ako

21
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,580
upang kunin ang panukala ng Kanyang Grasya.

22
00:02:36,790 --> 00:02:37,860
ano yun?

23
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,900
Bawat daang taon,

24
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,510
Hawak ng kanyang Grace

25
00:02:41,510 --> 00:02:42,350
isang Void Tournament.

26
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:43,790
Sa araw na iyon,

27
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,740
anumang espiritu ay maaaring hamunin siya.

28
00:02:46,740 --> 00:02:47,580
Kung manalo sila,

29
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:49,180
Ang kanyang Grasya ay nagbubunga

30
00:02:49,510 --> 00:02:50,350
ang trono sa kanila.

31
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:51,630
At kung matatalo sila?

32
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:52,980
Kung matalo sila,

33
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,700
naghihintay sila sa susunod na siglo

34
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:57,550
at subukan muli.

35
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:04,460
nakikita ko.

36
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:07,580
Hindi nakakagulat

37
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,740
iba ang pakiramdam ng lungsod.

38
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:13,630
Simu,

39
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:16,830
bakit gaganapin ang tournament na ito?

40
00:03:17,210 --> 00:03:18,070
Ang mga pagnanasa ng mga espiritu

41
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:19,740
hinding-hindi mabubura.

42
00:03:21,110 --> 00:03:21,990
Sa halip na pigilan sila,

43
00:03:22,270 --> 00:03:24,110
mas mabuting hayaan silang gumawa ng gulo.

44
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:26,020
Hindi ko sila papayagan

45
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:27,110
patuloy mo akong sinusubukang patayin.

46
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:29,860
Ngunit ang iyong kapangyarihan

47
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:31,020
humina na.

48
00:03:31,950 --> 00:03:32,990
Paano mo sila haharapin?

49
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:37,420
Maaari mong pakiramdam

50
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,300
nagbago ang kapangyarihan ko?

51
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:41,390
Nararamdaman ko

52
00:03:42,830 --> 00:03:43,700
na lumaki ka na

53
00:03:44,830 --> 00:03:45,700
medyo mahina.

54
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:50,540
Ito ay wala.

55
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:53,020
Ang Fusang Tree ay naibalik.

56
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:55,510
Next, breath regulation lang ang kailangan ko.

57
00:03:56,070 --> 00:03:56,990
kakayanin ko.

58
00:03:58,015 --> 00:03:59,112
Kung malalaman nila yan

59
00:03:59,123 --> 00:03:59,963
sa panahon ng paligsahan,

60
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:02,460
ano ang gagawin ng iyong mga ambisyosong courtier

61
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:04,140
gawin pagkatapos?

62
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,830
Kahit magkasama, hindi sila bagay sa akin.

63
00:04:08,990 --> 00:04:10,700
Pero kung hindi ako magpapakita,

64
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,208
malalaman nila agad

65
00:04:13,219 --> 00:04:13,900
anong nangyayari.

66
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:15,860
Noon,

67
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,710
higit sa kalahati ng mga espiritu

68
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,940
ay pagkatapos ng aking buhay.

69
00:04:25,590 --> 00:04:26,430
Kaya,

70
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:29,830
kailangan mong magpakita?

71
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,070
tama yan.

72
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:34,110
Ano ang dahilan kung bakit hindi ka pumunta?

73
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:37,380
Walang makakapigil sa akin.

74
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,300
Ako ang iyong spell bearer.

75
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:41,780
At hindi kita mapipigilan?

76
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:45,350
Anong kinalaman niyan?

77
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,460
Ikaw naman,

78
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:51,700
nitong mga nakaraang araw,

79
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:54,180
araw-araw kang nauubusan.

80
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:56,060
Ang Void ba ay nakakaakit sa iyo?

81
00:05:01,150 --> 00:05:02,260
Hindi ka ginagamit

82
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:04,740
sa kawalan ko diba?

83
00:05:06,710 --> 00:05:07,550
Bantayan mo ang iyong dila.

84
00:05:08,420 --> 00:05:09,270
Dapat hinayaan na kita

85
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,740
patuloy na dumaranas ng malamig na lason.

86
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,300
Pakikalma ang iyong galit.

87
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:15,150
Nagjo-joke lang ako kanina.

88
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,180
Lumabas na ako

89
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,140
para sa mismong bagay na ito.

90
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,690
Ilang araw na kitang pinoproblema,

91
00:05:39,277 --> 00:05:40,610
kaya may gusto akong ibigay sayo.

92
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,470
Ginawa ko ito para sa iyo.

93
00:05:42,470 --> 00:05:45,500
♪Dumating ang tagsibol; natunaw ang yelo at niyebe♪

94
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,490
♪Nagising ang lahat, kasama ang hanging silangan♪

95
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:51,960
ayoko

96
00:05:51,970 --> 00:05:53,420
isang walang kabuluhang bagay.

97
00:05:56,340 --> 00:06:00,110
♪Sa buong panahon♪

98
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:01,470
Pinaghirapan ko ito.

99
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,740
Mangyaring tanggapin ito, Your Grace.

100
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:08,270
♪Ang lumang gabi♪

101
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:19,680
♪Hiram ng mortal na init para maibsan ang lamig♪

102
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:27,070
♪Ang maiinit na hangin ay nagdudulot ng mabangong pamumulaklak♪

103
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:34,350
♪Hayaan mo akong magmahal nang buong puso
sa kagandahang-loob ng kabataan♪

104
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:38,100
♪Na may magaan, walang pakialam na mga salita♪

105
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:42,970
♪Nagniningning pa rin♪

106
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:47,300
Medyo gumaling ka na.

107
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:48,870
Malapit na,

108
00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:50,740
gagaling ang malamig mong lason.

109
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:56,080
♪Ang maikling buhay ay nangangahas na hanapin ang kawalang-hanggan♪

110
00:06:56,230 --> 00:06:57,150
Pero nararamdaman ko

111
00:06:58,300 --> 00:06:59,740
gumastos ka na naman ng maraming espiritu.

112
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:03,610
♪Hiram ng isang magandang panaginip♪

113
00:07:04,710 --> 00:07:05,820
Huwag mo akong usisain.

114
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,100
hindi ko kaya yun.

115
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,940
Ang buhay ko ay nakasalalay sa iyo.

116
00:07:12,150 --> 00:07:13,663
Kung may mangyari sa tournament,

117
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:14,580
Mawawalan ako ng kanlungan,

118
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:16,700
at wawakasan muna ako ng Kanang Kamay.

119
00:07:18,710 --> 00:07:20,350
At least alam mo ang lugar mo.

120
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:25,780
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

121
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:31,880
♪Nakikita ko ang isang sinag♪

122
00:07:33,990 --> 00:07:36,570
♪Sa anong tahanan ako babalik♪

123
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,380
Ang boring.

124
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:09,740
(Gao Xuande, Ji Youming, Xiao Yuan)

125
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:10,700
(Jun Lin, Yin Lang, Gu Cangwu)

126
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:15,380
(Yin Lang)

127
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,220
