165
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:00,660
(Ayoko pa)

166
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:01,710
(upang maging Soberano.)

167
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:34,190
Halika, lumaban ka.

168
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:36,580
Lumaban.

169
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:38,190
Lumaban ka!

170
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:40,430
Bilisan mo.

171
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:44,140
Itinaas si Simu

172
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:45,350
ang curfew sa araw

173
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,430
ng Void Tournament

174
00:11:46,430 --> 00:11:47,500
at itakda ang mga posporo

175
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:48,900
sa ilalim ng kabilugan ng buwan,

176
00:11:49,190 --> 00:11:50,830
kaya ang mga espiritung ito

177
00:11:50,990 --> 00:11:52,990
ilalabas ang kanilang buong lakas.

178
00:11:53,470 --> 00:11:55,380
Ngayong gabi, kasisimula pa lang.

179
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:00,990
Wala na. huminto ako.

180
00:12:29,350 --> 00:12:30,660
Bago dumating ang mga espiritung ito,

181
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:32,190
lahat sila ay pumirma ng death waiver.

182
00:12:32,740 --> 00:12:33,740
Mag-aaway sila

183
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,470
hanggang kamatayan.

184
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:37,340
Nasaan si Simu?

185
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:39,710
Hindi ba narito ang mga espiritung ito
para hamunin siya?

186
00:12:42,110 --> 00:12:43,620
Napakaraming espiritu

187
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:44,460
nagpapaligsahan para sa kanyang upuan.

188
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:45,990
Kung haharapin sila ni Simu isa-isa,

189
00:12:45,990 --> 00:12:46,830
mapapagod siya.

190
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:48,620
Ang mga preliminaries

191
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,740
nagsimula kaninang umaga.

192
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:51,660
Ang mga martial contestant

193
00:12:51,830 --> 00:12:52,860
lumaban sa isang suntukan

194
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:54,020
at humarap sa dalawa.

195
00:12:54,430 --> 00:12:56,020
Tanging ang huling sampung pares

196
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:57,310
kikita ng karapatan

197
00:12:57,310 --> 00:12:58,830
para harapin ng diretso si Simu.

198
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,340
Lahat,

199
00:13:07,470 --> 00:13:09,950
tapos na ang preliminaries.

200
00:13:20,310 --> 00:13:21,260
Ano ang amoy na iyon?

201
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:29,110
Tama na ang oras.

202
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:30,710
Dapat nandito si Simu.

203
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:33,100
Tingnan mo.

204
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:33,950
Mabilis.

205
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:34,800
It's Her Grace.

206
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,900
Nandito na si Grace.

207
00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:37,830
Ang kanyang Grace.

208
00:13:37,830 --> 00:13:38,740
Nandito na si Grace.

209
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:19,020
Huwag tayong mag aksaya ng oras.

210
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:21,070
Sabay lapit sa akin.

211
00:14:41,470 --> 00:14:42,310
Your Grace,

212
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:43,430
kahanga-hanga!

213
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:45,430
Kung sino man ang makatalo sa akin ngayon

214
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:47,740
aangkinin ang upuan

215
00:14:48,310 --> 00:14:49,190
ng Soberano.

216
00:15:05,950 --> 00:15:07,230
Ako si Wu Kui.

217
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:09,020
Pagbati, Your Grace.

218
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:10,460
Wu Kui. Gumagawa na siya ng move.

219
00:15:10,990 --> 00:15:11,830
Sa ngayon, siya lang

220
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:12,900
makakapantay sa Her Grace.

221
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,320
Wu Kui.

222
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,160
Si Wu Kui ay kakila-kilabot.

223
00:15:15,160 --> 00:15:16,350
- Eksakto.
- Talaga.

224
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:17,310
Panoorin mong mabuti.

225
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:18,190
Si Wu Kui iyon.

226
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:23,470
100 taon na ang nakalipas.

227
00:15:23,950 --> 00:15:25,230
Medyo lumakas ka.

228
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:26,700
Salamat, Your Grace.

229
00:15:27,380 --> 00:15:28,220
Pagkatapos,

230
00:15:28,590 --> 00:15:29,430
patawarin mo ako.

231
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:40,153
Malakas ang espiritung ito,

232
00:15:40,473 --> 00:15:41,782
iba sa mga karibal dati.

233
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:42,700
Syempre.

234
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:44,140
Siya ay dating Panginoon

235
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:45,590
ng Zhuangling Temple.

236
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:49,310
Ang mga espiritu ng Zhuangling Temple

237
00:15:50,990 --> 00:15:53,430
lahat ay naghahangad ng kapangyarihan, lalo na si Wu Kui.

238
00:15:54,430 --> 00:15:56,660
Matapos maging Soberano si Simu,

239
00:15:57,660 --> 00:15:59,380
dumating siya para hamunin siya
hindi mabilang na beses.

240
00:16:00,110 --> 00:16:01,070
Pagkatapos ng bawat pagkatalo,

241
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:03,140
nagbitiw siya at pumunta

242
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:05,430
sa North Sea para magsanay.

243
00:16:06,620 --> 00:16:07,950
Hindi niya hinahamon si Simu

244
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:09,593
para sa posisyon ng Soberano,

245
00:16:09,950 --> 00:16:11,470
ngunit upang maging pinakamalakas.

246
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:53,820
Sa 300 taon na ito,

247
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:54,950
ikaw ang una

248
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:56,630
para umabot hanggang dito.

249
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:58,300
Nambobola mo ako.

250
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:28,740
Hindi mo ako matatalo.

251
00:18:29,150 --> 00:18:30,470
Bumalik sa susunod na siglo.

252
00:18:30,870 --> 00:18:31,710
Your Grace,

253
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:33,300
mananalo ba ako

254
00:18:33,990 --> 00:18:35,260
sa susunod na siglo?

255
00:18:41,820 --> 00:18:43,780
Bakit kailangan mong kumilos sa salpok?

256
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:46,420
Your Grace,

257
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:48,990
pagkatapos ng aking huling pagkatalo, nalutas ko

258
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:51,100
na sa pagkakataong ito,

259
